title: Effect on existing ordinances
context: [§46-147] Effect on existing ordinances. This part shall not invalidate any impact fee ordinance existing on June 19, 1992. [L 1992, c 282, pt of §2] Revision Note &ldquo;Part&rdquo; substituted for &ldquo;chapter&rdquo;. &ldquo;June 19, 1992&rdquo; substituted for &ldquo;the effective date of this Act&rdquo;.
